# Cloudy Music Lab ðŸŽ¶

Cloudy Music Lab is an iOS app for indie artists to explore creative music-making. Features include audio playback, mood-based tagging, and AI lyric prototyping.

## Features
- Audio playback with mood tagging
- AI-powered lyric generation (mock API)
- Offline-friendly, clean SwiftUI interface
- Local storage of track metadata

## Architecture
- MVVM using SwiftUI
- AVFoundation for audio
- Codable for mock API
- UserDefaults for early local storage (Core Data or FileManager later)

## Setup
1. Open the project in Xcode
2. Run on iPhone simulator or physical device
3. Start building!

